attributes.review: When you first open the app it is way too bright. You see i’m a vampire and light isn’t the best thing for me. I am also very allergic to oranges and there seems to be an orange in the front page. I could just smell my allergies coming through the screen. So, truly i feel like this app is really badly planned out and needs to work on the brightness of colors. 100/10 don’t recommend !!!
